name: Tic Tac Toe: Speed Tapping
storyline:
The rules are the same as in tic-tac-toe.
Tap blocks to get them.
The first player to get a block in any one row (vertical, horizontal, or diagonal) wins!
Tap a block that has been taken once to get it back!
summary:
Tic-tac-toe in a game of speed!
The one with the fastest tap and the smartest brain wins!
